      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a0",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1428584858,
      "version": 228,
      "versionNonce": 1118949235,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774287182621,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "flow.kickoff()\n        ↓\nget_topic()          ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\ngenerate_draft()     ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\nreview_draft()       ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\n\"approved\" or \"needs_revision\"  ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\nFLOW ENDS ← that's it! top to bottom, done!",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "flow.kickoff()\n        ↓\nget_topic()          ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\ngenerate_draft()     ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\nreview_draft()       ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\n\"approved\" or \"needs_revision\"  ← fires once ✅\n        ↓\nFLOW ENDS ← that's it! top to bottom, done!",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8LUPXaxr1vH1ktkh_4Ux8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 237.10934448242188,
      "y": 512.6041618188226,
      "width": 499.8597412109375,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 869157082,
      "version": 144,
      "versionNonce": 2104373723,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774285221665,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "So when you call self.generate_draft() directly:\npython@listen(\"needs_revision\")\ndef revise(self, result):\n    return self.generate_draft(self.state.topic)\n    # ↑ just a python function call\n    # flow already completed its top to bottom run\n    # no events fire\n    # flow doesn't restart\n    # stops here ❌",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "So when you call self.generate_draft() directly:\npython@listen(\"needs_revision\")\ndef revise(self, result):\n    return self.generate_draft(self.state.topic)\n    # ↑ just a python function call\n    # flow already completed its top to bottom run\n    # no events fire\n    # flow doesn't restart\n    # stops here ❌",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "54toApQszcjbKfSPgmvqN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 261.640625,
      "y": 836.8098726537503,
      "width": 599.9796142578125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
